            ]
          }
        ],
        "orig": "Diploma in Engineering under Lateral Entry scheme from ITIs, is a regular course, hence all In-service candidates have to submit 'No Objection Certificate' fiom their present employer to the office of the Central Selection Committee (CSC) at Birchandra State Central Library on 4th and 5'h October 2A21 from 11.00 A.M to 4.00 PM. Further, such candidates also have to produce  their 'Release Order' fiom their employer at the time of admission in respective  Polytechnic  Institutes. Otherwise, their candidature will not be considered  and their admission  will not be confirmed.",
        "text": "Diploma in Engineering under Lateral Entry scheme from ITIs, is a regular course, hence all In-service candidates have to submit 'No Objection Certificate' fiom their present employer to the office of the Central Selection Committee (CSC) at Birchandra State Central Library on 4th and 5'h October 2A21 from 11.00 A.M to 4.00 PM. Further, such candidates also have to produce  their 'Release Order' fiom their employer at the time of admission in respective  Polytechnic  Institutes. Otherwise, their candidature will not be considered  and their admission  will not be confirmed."
